<i>noun</i>: 자유방임 [자유방임], 불간섭 [불간섭] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자유방임 [자유방임]</dt><br>
<dd>1. noninterference; laissez faire</dd><br>
<dd>각자의 자유에 맡겨 간섭하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of respecting others' freedom and not interfering in their business.</dd><br>
<dd>2. noninterference; laissez faire</dd><br>
<dd>국가의 간섭을 배제하고 개인의 경제 활동의 자유를 최대한 보장하려는 경제 사상에 찬성하는 주장.</dd><br>
<dd>An opinion that agrees to the economic idea of trying to eliminate the state's intervention in the economy and to guarantee individuals the freedom of economic activities to the maximum extent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>불간섭 [불간섭]</dt><br>
<dd>noninterference</dd><br>
<dd>남의 일에 끼어들거나 참견하지 않음.</dd><br>
<dd>The practice of not interfering in others' matter.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>